        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="LeetCode-169-解題紀錄"><a href="#LeetCode-169-解題紀錄" class="headerlink" title="LeetCode 169 解題紀錄"></a>LeetCode 169 解題紀錄</h1><h2 id="題目資訊"><a href="#題目資訊" class="headerlink" title="題目資訊"></a>題目資訊</h2><ul><li>題號：LeetCode 169  </li><li>難度：#Easy  </li><li>使用技巧：#HashMap</li></ul><h2 id="題目說明"><a href="#題目說明" class="headerlink" title="題目說明"></a>題目說明</h2><p>找出陣列中出現次數超過一半的元素。</p><h2 id="範例"><a href="#範例" class="headerlink" title="範例"></a>範例</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Input: nums = [<span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>]</span><br><span class="line">Output: <span class="number">3</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="🔍-解題思路"><a href="#🔍-解題思路" class="headerlink" title="🔍 解題思路"></a>🔍 解題思路</h2><ol><li>使用 <code>dict</code> 統計每個元素的出現次數。</li><li>遍歷字典，檢查是否有元素出現次數 &gt; <code>len(nums) // 2</code>。</li><li>找到符合條件的元素即為「多數元素」，回傳它。</li></ol><p>此方法屬於經典「雜湊統計」技巧，簡單有效！</p><hr><h2 id="🛠️-技巧筆記"><a href="#🛠️-技巧筆記" class="headerlink" title="🛠️ 技巧筆記"></a>🛠️ 技巧筆記</h2><table><thead><tr><th>方法</th><th>用途說明</th><th>範例程式碼</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>.get(key, default)</code></td><td>取出 key 的值，若 key 不存在則回傳預設值（如 0）</td><td><code>maps.get(i, 0)</code></td></tr><tr><td><code>.items()</code></td><td>取得 dict 中所有 <code>(key, value)</code> 組</td><td><code>for key, value in maps.items():</code></td></tr></tbody></table><hr><h2 id="👣-解題步驟示範（以-nums-3-2-3-為例）"><a href="#👣-解題步驟示範（以-nums-3-2-3-為例）" class="headerlink" title="👣 解題步驟示範（以 nums &#x3D; [3, 2, 3] 為例）"></a>👣 解題步驟示範（以 nums &#x3D; [3, 2, 3] 為例）</h2><ol><li><p>初始化空字典：</p> <figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">maps = &#123;&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>統計每個元素出現的次數：</p> <figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> nums:</span><br><span class="line">    maps[i] = maps.get(i, <span class="number">0</span>) + <span class="number">1</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>字典統計結果如下：</p> <figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">maps = &#123;<span class="number">3</span>: <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">2</span>: <span class="number">1</span>&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>找出出現次數大於 <code>len(nums) // 2</code> 的元素：</p> <figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> key, value <span class="keyword">in</span> maps.items():</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> value &gt; <span class="built_in">len</span>(nums) // <span class="number">2</span>:</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> key</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><hr><h2 id="✅-完整程式碼"><a href="#✅-完整程式碼" class="headerlink" title="✅ 完整程式碼"></a>✅ 完整程式碼</h2><pre><code class="language-python">def majorityElement(nums):    maps = &#123;&#125;    for i in nums:        maps[i] = maps.get(i, 0) + 1    for key, value in maps.items():        if value &gt; len(nums) // 2:            return key</code></pre>]]></content>
      
      
